comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Payne's (PHX) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Crowder (PHX) clamps Carter Jr.'s (ORL) upper body underneath the basket and the contact affects his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Wagner's (ORL) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Bamba (ORL) briefly places his hand to Payne's (PHX) side during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Bamba (ORL) slides his forearm to Ayton's (PHX) front and makes marginal contact contesting his shot attempt at the basket.
Hampton (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Ayton's (PHX) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Carter Jr. (ORL) lifts his pivot foot after his gather.
Ayton (PHX) places his hand to Carter Jr.'s (ORL) side defending his drive to basket and makes marginal contact defending his shot attempt.
Shamet (PHX) and Bamba (ORL) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Crowder (PHX) places his hand to Bamba's (ORL) side after his gather and marginal contact occurs during his shot attempt at the basket.
Ayton (PHX) makes incidental contact to Carter's (ORL) shoulder area as both players are reaching for the rebound.
Bamba (ORL) makes marginal contact to Ayton's (PHX) side underneath the basket and disengages as they pursue the loose ball.
Hampton (ORL) and Payne (PHX) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to PHX.
Hampton (ORL) places his forearm to Payne's (PHX) front during his drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs.
Payne (PHX) places a bent forearm to Hampton's (ORL) side as he braces for the contact and releases as he comes to a pause during his drive.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Bridges' (PHX) path and absorbs the contact.
Crowder (PHX) makes marginal contact to Anthony's (ORL) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Payne (PHX) places his forearm to Hampton's (ORL) side as he goes to, not through his space and releases away from the contact.
Hampton (ORL) places his hand to Payne's (PHX) front as he defends over the pick and makes marginal contact as he slides his hand off.
Ayton (PHX) is already in Hampton's (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Carter Jr. (ORL) places his forearm to Payne's (PHX) front defending his drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs.
Carter Jr. (ORL) places a resting hand to Ayton's (PHX) side and does not apply force  contesting his shot attempt.
Crowder (PHX) briefly engages with Wagner (ORL) after the screen and disengages.
Bridges (PHX) commits a take foul on Anthony (ORL).
Anthony (ORL) commits a take foul on Shamet (PHX).
Anthony (ORL) commits a take foul on Payne (PHX).
Wagner (ORL) slightly extends his arm against Bridges' (PHX) backside and makes marginal contact as he slides his hand off.
Bridges (PHX) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Wagner (ORL).
